      "id": "our-story",
      "title": "Our Story",
      "icon": "üíë",
      "order": 2,
      "content": {
        "howWeMet": {
          "title": "How We Met",
            "story": "About two years ago, amidst demanding schedules and the echoes of past challenges, fate orchestrated a beautiful beginning...",
            "detail-story": [
            "---",
            "## Our Story: A Serendipitous Melody",
            "",
            "A little over two years ago, amidst demanding schedules and the echoes of life's tumultuous currents, fate orchestrated a beautiful beginning. One of us, seeking solace and respite, decided to play a live gig with a senior colleague. That same night, the other, weary from work, chose to unwind at that very show.",
            "",
            "Across the room, our eyes met. He was striking and quiet, dressed in a black polo shirt, his fingers expertly placed on the guitar frets. She was vibrant and serene, seated in the audience, her eyes sparkling with appreciation as the music filled the room. We exchanged only a brief \"hi\" that night, a prelude to what was to come. The first two encounters, however, were merely fleeting greetings.",
            "",
            "It was at a third, pivotal session‚Äîan album launch for a mutual friend and fellow band member‚Äîthat destiny truly intervened. This time, he wasn't on stage with his guitar. Instead, we found ourselves on opposite bar stools, where he truly went to work, weaving a witty and captivating conversation. Though she tried to hold back, he seemed to read her soul, and amidst the evening's festivities, we even shared a casual dance. On this memorable evening, the conversation deepened, numbers were exchanged, and from that moment, our unprecedented union unknowingly began.",
            "",
            "Our shared passion for music quickly became the cornerstone of our bond. He, with his love for instruments, and she, a gifted vocalist and music minister, found harmony in melodies. Then, we discovered another shared delight: food. She, a magnificent chef, and he, a discerning lover of good meals, found joy in the culinary arts. His first taste of her cooking, jollof rice and vegetable soup with assorted meat and fried fish, was sumptuous to say the least.",
            "",
            "Our friendship deepened over a year and a half, a symphony of shared interests and growing affection. As our connection evolved, we both recognized a future together, a future that brought us to this incredible day. The rest, as they say, is history in the making."
            ],
          "date": "2023",
          "location": "Norcross, Georgia"
        },
